cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) - The paper proposes a model for color labeling of semantic parts of people in videos, which is a common problem in computer vision. 
2. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The proposed model is based on binary search trees and a large peer-labelled color name dataset, which involves machine learning and artificial intelligence techniques. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper mentions the use of learnt features that are not explainable, indicating the involvement of machine learning techniques. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The proposed model is applied to person search in videos, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper evaluates the proposed solution on person search datasets, which involves information retrieval techniques.
